{"tid":1987751,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"telegram 已經唔安全，請大家轉用signal","createTime":"2020-04-24T16:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T18:08:24.000Z","uid":266212,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f95a9aea6528b65beb29de5d46292b29ee002f43","tid":1987751,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"telegram 原來default唔加密，公海仲要加唔到密。<br />\n唔該大家有緊要野用signal。<br />\n<br />\n連snowden都用signal，你話安唔安全？"},{"pid":"3b72decaa60c4634ec732a9f93f4db478ed9f48c","tid":1987751,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"但係要用太空卡reg個acct"},{"pid":"0139d53cc45d317285180f2b05e8f1b72e81f569","tid":1987751,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"工作小組希望香港市民留意以下幾個要點：<br />\n<br />\n1）工作小組近日與不願具名的業界人士溝通後，確認 2020 年 4 月份版本的數位鑑證套裝軟件（包括 Cellebrite PA 及 UFED 等），能夠擷取部分 Android 及 iOS 裝置內，Telegram 的所有現存及已刪除對話內容。另外，業界人士亦確認 2019 年 12 月份版本的散列演算法軟件，已經能夠解開 Android 及 iOS 的 Telegram 客戶端密碼（亦稱 App passcode）。<br />\n<br />\n2）工作小組與資訊安全工程師溝通後，未有發現任何高重要度的 CVE，同時亦未有發現通訊協定有即時的安全隱憂。工作小組認爲目前而言，Telegram 使用者之間的通訊依然安全。<br />\n<br />\n3）工作小組與資訊安全工程師測試後，發現漏洞編號 CVE-2019-15514 依然能夠於部分 Telegram 使用者身上重現，即表示有部分香港市民與使用 Telegram 時候，未有選擇隱藏電話號碼。工作小組憂慮，按照目前香港的政治及社會局勢，這個功能漏洞會被不法分子利用，從而被揭露未曾公開的個人私隱資料(NIST CWE-200)。<br />\n<br />\n4）工作小組亦提醒香港市民，有鑑於 Telegram 的資料庫已經能夠被鑑證軟件輕易破解，如果有需要交換敏感訊息，建議改爲使用 Signal。<br />\n<br />\nSignal 下載地址：<br />\nAndroid // <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.thoughtcrime.securesms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dorg.thoughtcrime.securesms&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=c53f4739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.thoughtcrime.securesms</a><br />\niOS // <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/signal-private-messenger/id874139669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fsignal-private-messenger%2Fid874139669&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=1812b13c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/signal-private-messenger/id874139669</a>"},{"pid":"d884d1b305ccc0234d0f7b5379afb18356dffb4a","tid":1987751,"uid":41458,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"You are fake news<br />\ntg 所有msg 都有加密，secret chat 用更勁嘅加密方法，只有雙方可睇到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6tSQWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6tSQWm.jpg&h=183238ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d31b183dc4ba2d840068487c6d70111b370b5b5","tid":1987751,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d884d1b305ccc0234d0f7b5379afb18356dffb4a","tid":1987751,"uid":41458,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"You are fake news<br />\ntg 所有msg 都有加密，secret chat 用更勁嘅加密方法，只有雙方可睇到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6tSQWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6tSQWm.jpg&h=183238ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VVxQYG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VVxQYG.jpg&h=0e122ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20454b4d3d7db701000e9310f94587b41ea6c8e7","tid":1987751,"uid":41458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d31b183dc4ba2d840068487c6d70111b370b5b5","tid":1987751,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d884d1b305ccc0234d0f7b5379afb18356dffb4a","tid":1987751,"uid":41458,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"You are fake news<br />\ntg 所有msg 都有加密，secret chat 用更勁嘅加密方法，只有雙方可睇到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6tSQWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6tSQWm.jpg&h=183238ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VVxQYG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VVxQYG.jpg&h=0e122ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔好quote 呢D 新聞網，假料<br />\n<br />\nAll Telegram messages are always securely encrypted. Messages in Secret Chats use client-client encryption, while Cloud Chats use client-server/server-client encryption and are stored encrypted in the Telegram Cloud (more here). This enables your cloud messages to be both secure and immediately accessible from any of your devices &ndash; even if you lose your device altogether.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/faq#q-why-not-just-make-all-chats-secret\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Ffaq%23q-why-not-just-make-all-chats-secret&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=f49acbfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/faq#q-why-not-just-make-all-chats-secret</a>"},{"pid":"60cc4554726cb86e1a31233ad196c6fa0cf6cead","tid":1987751,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:36:15.000Z","msg":"tg delete 功能垃圾，呢個理由夠未<br />\n不過有好多其他app<br />\nsignal/wickr/viber/dust/...........<br />\n大路app，就多人研究點去破解<br />\ntg 爆咗就一早嘅事"},{"pid":"437b25a64afbd1657190b2e88ec0b5dea4732fbb","tid":1987751,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"signal 都唔係好選擇<br />\npopo買個tool 破解到signal<br />\n要安全自己用數學加密會好好多"},{"pid":"dc4f67432d6a39580703520c5e74e7a050b4d3a7","tid":1987751,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"tg 先係大伏講真<br />\n<br />\n一直吹到好安全 其實只係限住坊間<br />\n<br />\n去到政府級別介入就同whatsapp無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇韓國n號房單野就知  全部會員資料政府都可以拎到"},{"pid":"a66b3cb87e732a55cf